Expected effect:

When the width of ToolStripLabel is not enough, this control can use ellipsis to display content that is not wide enough.

p.s:

If you don't see the issue, it may be that your computer font is different from the font I used. Adjust the width of the Form to 500, or 400, and it can be displayed.
